很高兴。</div>\n<div>我想证明自己的努力会被回报。</div>\n<div>还不结束。</div>\n<div>正因为是选拔和下垂都能理解双方的心情的自己，所以</div>\n<div>我想从这里能看到的东西有很多。</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>然后最后给粉丝们。</div>\n<div>其实，我想向每个人道谢。然后也想说对不起。</div>\n<div>说不定能把“粉丝们”叫出来，说实话真的很失礼，所以不知道。</div>\n<div>既然大家都在想，我就相信一个人，相信大家。</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>所以，也请相信我。</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>大家都理解我的心情，互相分享。</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>如果我感到不甘心的话，我会一起后悔的。</div>\n<div>但是，我不想再让粉丝们后悔了。</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>我会竭尽全力努力做自己能做的。绝对。约定。</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>总是很难。</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><img src=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/photos/entry/2012/03/20/7086889/0001.jpeg\" width=\"240\"></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><img src=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/photos/entry/2012/03/20/7086889/0002.gif\"><img src=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/photos/entry/2012/03/20/7086889/0003.gif\"><img src=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/photos/entry/2012/03/20/7086889/0004.gif\"></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div align=\"right\">sayunyanヽ</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><img src=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/photos/entry/2012/03/20/7086889/0005.gif\"></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\t\t</div>","transTitle":"最大的对手=自己+ +","url":"http://blog.nogizaka46.com/sayuri.inoue/smph/2012/03/003636.php"}